Package dog.giraffe.image

Abstractions to read, transform, and write images.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Image
    An image is a rectangle of vectors.
    Image.Reader
    A Reader contains all information to read a line of the image.
    ImageReader
    An image that can be closed.
    ImageWriter
    Class to create images as BufferedImages and to write to disk.
    ImageWriter.Factory
    Factory for ImageWriters.
    ImageWriter.Line
    Contains all the information to write one line of the image.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BufferedImageReader
    An ImageWriter that reads line from a memory buffer.
    BufferedImageWriter
    An ImageWriter that writes to an internal memory buffer.
    FileImageReader
    An ImageReader that reads every line directly from disk.
    FileImageWriter
    An ImageWriter that writes an image line by line to the disk directly.
    Image.Abstract
    Implementation of some trivial methods.
    Image.Abstract.Dimensions  
    Image.Transform
    A Image.Transform is an image which performs some operation on a line read before returning it to the caller.
    Images
    Helper methods for the creation of images.
    PrepareImages
    Helper class to correctly Image.prepare(Context, Continuation) a DAG of images.
